  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}Daaamn, this is some primo sushi![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}The slices are huge![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}Man, I'm starving. Can we eat?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 8 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}Hey, where are Aigis-san and Ikutsuki-san?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}He took her to the lab for a tune-up or something.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}He said they'll join us later.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}Hehe, the chairman just can't stay away from the lab, can he?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}That must be my father.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}We've been waiting for you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}So it's finally over, then.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}That's right.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 8 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}Wh-Who's he?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Can't ya tell? That's Kirijo-senpai's dad. She looks exactly like him.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 8 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}Y-You think so?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Congratulations, everyone. You've done well. No words can express my gratitude.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}Though you'll never receive the recognition you deserve, your achievement was truly monumental.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}Thank you, really.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 18 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}To you, I owe a special thanks.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}For lending us your power until the very end.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Oh, i-it was no big deal.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}Thanks to you, the twelve Shadows behind all this chaos have been destroyed.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}You've carried this burden long enough. You deserve a chance to experience the joys of youth.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}As of midnight tonight, the Specialized Extracurricular Execution Squad will be disbanded.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}Disbanded...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MSG_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}Oh, right...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="21" name="MSG_021_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}No longer must you risk your lives in battle.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}Tomorrow, you can triumphantly return to a normal school life.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="22" name="MSG_022_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 224 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 29 0 0}...Is something the matter?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="23" name="MSG_023_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}Ah, it's nothin'.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="24" name="MSG_024_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 31 0 0}All right, everyone. It's time to celebrate.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 32 0 0}Your feast awaits. And don't worry about holding back. Eat as much as you'd like![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="25" name="MSG_025_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 33 0 0}Sweet! Freakin' finally![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
